                    <p>天猫【依视路旗舰店】</p><p>依视路 · 钻晶 X4 防蓝光近视眼镜（1.60）日常大促价 1880 元，今日下单立减 282 元。</p><p>领取 1233 元大额券 + 70 元淘礼金红包 + 15 元天猫服饰券（系统自动发放）。</p><p><span class="font-color-red"><strong>点击详情页右上角【...】，选择【淘金币】</strong></span>，淘金币可抵 8 元。</p><p>88 会员凑单 138 元以上商品，可用满 480-60 元消费券，到手价 230.72 元起：</p><dir><a contenteditable="false" href="https://uland.taobao.com/coupon/edetail?traceId=215046e817810782267921126e0bda&amp;srItem=1&amp;e=TDO8OEuF3telhHvvyUNXZfh8CuWt5YH5OVuOuRD5gLJMmdsrkidbOWBzzpT26idJkYNN9IUeUr%2FNa6yhTqJ%2Bog%2Fmm6S7OrYIPFM4sbuLyqamKZTGh4rB2ROY9o8077DtRSHvQe2jOLZ9pbNCYX0I%2BPP%2BWUTgK%2F%2B0DI9LnV2RxzN7CtXivpqDNR2MV2VkCo%2BFQ6SUHSXO4YlgcK6iYH005xHtR5M9fhgNtsfGA5CFJLDe4LCSMIu01NeqSq5uaIh97jKjAO7pxYgdIMeVz1KiUQXqkCOsjO26LAxUL%2FBw5cjKAfdRIoKuBMf3ch%2F%2FOwx2F9OzDXnA1VkCGruttYDvNg%3D%3D&amp;union_lens=lensId:TAPI@1781078226@216606b9_14ed_19eb088f7b3_3092@01" target="_blank"><span class="card main-site"><span class="card-logo"><img height="800" src="https://img.alicdn.com/bao/uploaded/i4/2758969522/O1CN017GJN7f2KD8H8v8MC3_!!0-item_pic.jpg" title="线下超千元：法国依视路・旗舰膜致 1.60 近视镜 231 元官方破冰新低" width="800" /></span><span class="card-info"><span class="card-title"><span class="mall-data">天猫</span><span class="card-name">依视路 钻晶 X4 旗舰眼镜</span></span><span class="card-abstract"> 1.60 防蓝光 含镜框</span><span class="card-controls"><span class="price">凑单后 230.72 元</span><span class="card-btn-deep">领 1233 元券</span></span></span></span></a></dir><dir><a contenteditable="false" href="https://uland.taobao.com/coupon/edetail?traceId=2150463c17810788411306247e0c6b&amp;srItem=1&amp;e=AuqNFfiIq2ylhHvvyUNXZfh8CuWt5YH551NtNRhtOmTBA53XDxB%2BXiK676mJBLmpk3VE%2Bshe0ftO6xZ5oL4cx9zgbTJQOR2k%2FcwIeu2A2LbabAJjl9LutePDifvsAOFUJGWkCcij2eyNz3dLhI%2BwTxZOiO7Y6SAHhJI%2Bw8zn%2BHwCb4RQkxOMvLavT4hIvbmu6gtcnW8CescvWnt0m32sXmM5eYF1QT88zm9Z8aPQgYRD6TM1M2v5G7%2FAUd2Xn3d%2BRpKLba1grHiF%2Br4RO79Axig%2BFdTYWssrmhX6HzpVvI6jGwG5%2FUm0S6J7%2BkHL3AEW&amp;union_lens=lensId:TAPI@1781078841@210569e9_1480_19eb0925772_0518@01" target="_blank"><span class="card main-site"><span class="card-logo"><img height="732" src="https://img.alicdn.com/i1/2222353991185/O1CN01Oq5EMw1KcmTRX9eE9~crop,34,0,732,732~_!!2222353991185.jpg" title="线下超千元：法国依视路・旗舰膜致 1.60 近视镜 231 元官方破冰新低" width="732" /></span><span class="card-info"><span class="card-title"><span class="mall-data">天猫</span><span class="card-name">示例凑单品 下单后可申请退款</span></span><span class="card-abstract"></span><span class="card-controls"><span class="price">加购物车 1 件</span><span class="card-btn-deep">直达链接</span></span></span></span></a></dir><p>X4 下单后提供配镜数据，免费升级钻晶膜致（详询客服）。</p><p style="text-align: center;"><img height="351" src="https://img.ithome.com/newsuploadfiles/2026/6/8631952f-3c1d-4963-b77e-438b4f24244b.jpg?x-bce-process=image/format,f_auto" title="线下超千元：法国依视路・旗舰膜致 1.60 近视镜 231 元官方破冰新低" width="1205" /></p><p>如果不知道怎么挑选镜框，可先摘下自己现在戴的眼镜，眼镜腿内侧会标有此镜架具体参数。</p><p>本次配镜赠镜框，且有钛 + 金属框可选（8g 起），共有 20 款可选，比较适合男生佩戴。</p><p>本次也支持来镜加工（需拍下后第一时间联系客服），<strong>非常适合华为 / 小米等智能眼镜配镜</strong>，比官方便宜非常多。</p><p style="text-align: center;"><img height="1093" src="https://img.ithome.com/newsuploadfiles/2025/8/c3dc8c79-5c11-4ac4-bcbc-77e1695988f8.png?x-bce-process=image/format,f_auto" title="线下超千元：法国依视路・旗舰膜致 1.60 近视镜 231 元官方破冰新低" width="1080" /></p><p>依视路钻晶 X4 镜片（1.60）官方定价 1880 元，钛 + 金属镜框日常 300~500 元不等。</p><p style="text-align: center;"><img height="246" src="https://img.ithome.com/newsuploadfiles/2025/8/a9819ef3-2099-4e58-ade0-bee605a26f54.png?x-bce-process=image/format,f_auto" title="线下超千元：法国依视路・旗舰膜致 1.60 近视镜 231 元官方破冰新低" width="988" /></p><blockquote><p style="text-align: left;">膜致是 X4 的全面升级款：</p><p style="text-align: left;">1.更耐磨：耐刮，耐高温提升 20%，特别适合户外使用；</p><p style="text-align: left;">2.更透亮：360° 减少反光技术，看东西更清澈（尤其开车，拍照场景）；</p><p style="text-align: left;">3.防蓝光更智能：阻隔有害蓝光的同时，保持镜片底色清透、看屏幕颜色更真实。</p></blockquote><p style="text-align: left;">小伙伴们如果不知道自己眼镜数据，可先下单，通知客服延迟发货，且支持随时退货（配镜后不支持）。</p><p>然后去附近的眼病医院或 3 甲医院，挂号验光，日常 50 元左右，数据也比较精确。</p><p>有了数据，今后也方便在网上配镜，便宜非常多。</p><p style="text-align: center;"><img height="1640" src="https://img.alicdn.com/imgextra/i3/2758969522/O1CN01F3tgLF2KD8QLJW79n_!!2758969522.jpg" title="线下超千元：法国依视路・旗舰膜致 1.60 近视镜 231 元官方破冰新低" width="1500" /></p><p>88 会员凑单 138 元以上商品，可用满 480-60 元消费券，到手价 230.72 元起：</p><dir><a contenteditable="false" href="https://uland.taobao.com/coupon/edetail?traceId=215046e817810782267921126e0bda&amp;srItem=1&amp;e=TDO8OEuF3telhHvvyUNXZfh8CuWt5YH5OVuOuRD5gLJMmdsrkidbOWBzzpT26idJkYNN9IUeUr%2FNa6yhTqJ%2Bog%2Fmm6S7OrYIPFM4sbuLyqamKZTGh4rB2ROY9o8077DtRSHvQe2jOLZ9pbNCYX0I%2BPP%2BWUTgK%2F%2B0DI9LnV2RxzN7CtXivpqDNR2MV2VkCo%2BFQ6SUHSXO4YlgcK6iYH005xHtR5M9fhgNtsfGA5CFJLDe4LCSMIu01NeqSq5uaIh97jKjAO7pxYgdIMeVz1KiUQXqkCOsjO26LAxUL%2FBw5cjKAfdRIoKuBMf3ch%2F%2FOwx2F9OzDXnA1VkCGruttYDvNg%3D%3D&amp;union_lens=lensId:TAPI@1781078226@216606b9_14ed_19eb088f7b3_3092@01" target="_blank"><span class="card main-site"><span class="card-logo"><img height="800" src="https://img.alicdn.com/bao/uploaded/i4/2758969522/O1CN017GJN7f2KD8H8v8MC3_!!0-item_pic.jpg" title="线下超千元：法国依视路・旗舰膜致 1.60 近视镜 231 元官方破冰新低" width="800" /></span><span class="card-info"><span class="card-title"><span class="mall-data">天猫</span><span class="card-name">依视路 钻晶 X4 旗舰眼镜</span></span><span class="card-abstract"> 1.60 防蓝光 含镜框</span><span class="card-controls"><span class="price">凑单后 230.72 元</span><span class="card-btn-deep">领 1233 元券</span></span></span></span></a></dir><dir><a contenteditable="false" href="https://uland.taobao.com/coupon/edetail?traceId=2150463c17810788411306247e0c6b&amp;srItem=1&amp;e=AuqNFfiIq2ylhHvvyUNXZfh8CuWt5YH551NtNRhtOmTBA53XDxB%2BXiK676mJBLmpk3VE%2Bshe0ftO6xZ5oL4cx9zgbTJQOR2k%2FcwIeu2A2LbabAJjl9LutePDifvsAOFUJGWkCcij2eyNz3dLhI%2BwTxZOiO7Y6SAHhJI%2Bw8zn%2BHwCb4RQkxOMvLavT4hIvbmu6gtcnW8CescvWnt0m32sXmM5eYF1QT88zm9Z8aPQgYRD6TM1M2v5G7%2FAUd2Xn3d%2BRpKLba1grHiF%2Br4RO79Axig%2BFdTYWssrmhX6HzpVvI6jGwG5%2FUm0S6J7%2BkHL3AEW&amp;union_lens=lensId:TAPI@1781078841@210569e9_1480_19eb0925772_0518@01" target="_blank"><span class="card main-